  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Women with monographically morbidly adherent placenta with or without a placenta
             previa.

          -  Scheduled delivery via cesarean hysterectomy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Delivery planned prior to 36 weeks (e.g. non-reassuring fetal status, preterm labor,
             severe preeclampsia, other medical/fetal indication for delivery as determined by the
             managing physician).
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
